title: Presidents Cup Capsules
text:
> Top News Presidents Cup Capsules International team player Louis Oosthuizen of South Africa and compatriot Branden Grace, right, celebrate after they defeated United States' Matt Kuchar and Patrick Reed 3 & 2 in their foursome match at the Presidents Cup golf tournament at the Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea, in Incheon, South Korea, Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015.(AP Photo/Ahn Young-joon)
